		<h2>Error Messages</h2>
		<p>
		  This page provides more detail on some of error messages RackMonkey reports. For errors with initial set up or 
		  databases, please consult troubleshooting.txt file included with RackMonkey.
		  For general information on using RackMonkey see <a href="<TMPL_VAR NAME=base_url>?view=help">Help Overview</a>.
		</p>
